	</element>
	<element name="Sentient Backpack" type="Magic Item" source="ToV Campaign Custom" id="ID_TOV_CAMPAIGN_MAGIC_ITEM_FFT_SENTIENTBACKPACK">
		<description>
			<p>A backpack is a leather pack carried on the back, typically with straps to secure it. A backpack can hold 1 cubic foot/ 30 pounds of gear.</p>
			<p class="indent">When filled with items, you can hear coughing from the backpack. It occationally throws up its contents.</p>
			<p class="indent">On the inside is a label of "Frankie's Funny Things".</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Wondrous Items</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">0</set>
			<set name="weight" lb="0">0 lb.</set>
			<set name="type">Wondrous Item</set>
			<set name="rarity">Unique</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
	<element name="Glasses of Hindsight" type="Magic Item" source="ToV Campaign Custom" id="ID_TOV_CAMPAIGN_MAGIC_ITEM_FFT_GLASSESOFHINDSIGHT">
		<description>
			<p>This pair of glasses lets you see things more clearly... after you have already messed them up.</p>
			<p class="indent">On the side you can spot an engraving of "Frankie's Funny Things".</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
